本書的改編電影《[[蘇珊夫人尋婚計|蘇珊夫人尋婚計]]》於2016年上映，由{{link-en|惠特·史蒂曼|Whit Stillman}}執導<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/whit-stillman-gearing-up-next-film-love-and-friendship-an-adaptation-of-jane-austens-lady-susan-20130718|title=Whit Stillman Gearing Up Next Film 'Love And Friendship,' An Adaptation Of Jane Austen's 'Lady Susan'|last=Jagernauth|first=Kevin|date=July 18, 2013|publisher=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|accessdate=February 14, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150427014028/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/whit-stillman-gearing-up-next-film-love-and-friendship-an-adaptation-of-jane-austens-lady-susan-20130718|archive-date=2015-04-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，女主角蘇珊夫人為[[凱特·貝琴薩|凱特·貝琴薩]]飾演。

